race.comment: MARAVICH (2) finally broke the maiden status when resuming and will have derived a stack of confidence from that breakthrough victory. Winning rider Lerena sticks in the saddle and should be going very close again. BOKUDEN (3) has placed three from four around this circuit and gets a bunch of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Will prove tough to hold out. KEY COMPONENT (8) looked handy saluting two back before not being too far away here last time out. In the mix. LOVE 'N' GAMES (5) is a winner here who broke back into the top-three last start when third at Lismore over 2120m. Can trouble the judge with luck in running.
